Steps :

▫️Launch EC2 Instance
Choose Ubuntu 22.04, t2.micro
Open Security Group → add inbound rule for port 5000 (TCP)

▫️Connect your EC2 (ssh)

▫️Paste these commands:
sudo apt update && sudo apt upgrade -y
sudo apt install python3-pip -y
pip3 install flask joblib scikit-learn numpy

scp -i your-key.pem titanic_model.pkl app.py ubuntu@<ec2-ip>:/home/ubuntu/

▫️create file named app.py and paste the app.py

▫️python3 app.py

▫️Test API
curl -X POST http://<ec2-public-ip>:5000/predict -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d "{\"features\": [3, 1, 22, 0, 0, 7.25]}"

▫️It should return:
{"prediction": 0}
